{"prompt": "Generate a website for a community non-profit. The website should be cozy and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Connect</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fef8f5;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #c0392b;\n            color: #fef8f5;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        main {\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            padding-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        }\n        section:last-child {\n            border-bottom: none;\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #c0392b;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        p {\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #e74c3c;\n            color: #fef8f5;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #a93126;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            background-color: #e74c3c;\n            color: #fef8f5;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #fef8f5;\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Community Connect</h1>\n        <p>Bringing people together, one connection at a time.</p>\n    </header>\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>At Community Connect, we believe in the power of local engagement to create a stronger, more vibrant neighborhood for everyone. We are a passionate group of volunteers dedicated to organizing events, supporting local initiatives, and fostering a sense of belonging among our residents.</p>\n            <p>From community gardens and neighborhood clean-ups to local workshops and social gatherings, we strive to make our community a warm and welcoming place to live.</p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"get-involved\">\n            <h2>Get Involved</h2>\n            <p>Your involvement is what makes our community thrive! Whether you have time to volunteer, a skill to share, or simply want to participate in our events, there are many ways to contribute.</p>\n            <p>Explore our upcoming events, learn about volunteer opportunities, or consider making a donation to help us continue our work.</p>\n            <button class=\"cta-button\" onclick=\"window.location.href='#contact'\">Support Us</button>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Have a question, suggestion, or want to learn more? Reach out to us!</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@communityconnect.org\">info@communityconnect.org</a></p>\n            <p>Follow us on social media for the latest updates!</p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Connect. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Designed with love for our community.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}